# gosu binary shipped with postgres:17 base image
# Compiled with Go v1.24.6 which has known stdlib vulnerabilities
# Remediation depends on postgres maintainers rebuilding gosu
# with an updated Go toolchain — no fix available from our side
# gosu only executes at container init for privilege dropping
# and is not exposed to network traffic or application input

